OL,3,CThe Body Shop owners set to call in
OL,4,Cadministrators
OL,6,FThe Body Shop is appointing
OL,7,Fadministrators with a restructure and
OL,8,Fstore losses likely, Rachel Younger
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FITV News has learned that the Body
OL,12,FShop has begun the process of filing
OL,13,Ffor administration.
OL,15,FThe business has been in trouble for
OL,16,Fsome time and a restructure is widely
OL,17,Fexpected to lead to shop closures and
OL,18,Fjob losses, as the administrators look
OL,19,Fto streamline the 200-plus stores in
OL,20,Fthe UK and announce a shift of focus
OL,21,Fto online sales.
