OL,3,CThe Body Shop owners set to call in
OL,4,Cadministrators
OL,6,FTrading over the key Christmas period
OL,7,Fand into January was not as strong as
OL,8,Fhoped.
OL,10,FThe business was founded by the late
OL,11,FDame Anita Roddick, who opened her
OL,12,Ffirst shop in Brighton in 1976.
OL,14,FThe brand describes itself as a "force
OL,15,Ffor good", and has marketed itself on
OL,16,Fethically sourced and naturally-based
OL,17,Fingredients from around the world.
OL,19,FIt was the first international beauty
OL,20,Fbrand to campaign against animal
OL,21,Ftesting in cosmetics.
