OL,3,CThe Body Shop owners set to call in
OL,4,Cadministrators
OL,6,FThe Body Shop was bought by private
OL,7,Fequity firm Aurelius just weeks ago.
OL,8,FIt has changed hands three times since
OL,9,Fit was sold by Dame Roddick in 2006,
OL,10,Fshortly before her death the following
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe brand was boycotted by some
OL,14,Fconsumers in 2006, after L'Oreal
OL,15,Fbought the company. People accused the
OL,16,Fcosmetics company of testing their
OL,17,Fproducts on animals.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/10
