OL,3,CThe Body Shop owners set to call in
OL,4,Cadministrators
OL,6,FIt is understood that the
OL,7,Fadministration process for its UK
OL,8,Foperations will not impact the brand's
OL,9,Fglobal franchise partners.
OL,11,FFor fashion columnist Sali Hughes, The
OL,12,FBody Shop was more than a cosmetics
OL,13,Fstore.
OL,15,F"A lot of the natural beauty products
OL,16,Fand beauty lines that we take for
OL,17,Fgranted now come from Anita Roddick
OL,18,Fand The Body Shop," she told ITV News.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/10
