OL,6,F"It really spearheaded the trend
OL,7,Ftowards natural and cruelty free
OL,8,Fproducts and sustainability as a whole.
OL,10,F"In a way its become a victim of its
OL,11,Fown success. It created a world that
OL,12,Fis now thriving. There are now natural
OL,13,F'clean' beauty products, the cruelty
OL,14,Ffree movement is massive.
OL,16,FFashion columnist Sali Hughes spoke to
OL,17,FITV News about how The Body Shop was
OL,18,Fmore than a cosmetics store for her
