OL,3,CThe Body Shop owners set to call in
OL,4,Cadministrators
OL,6,F"Everything that began with Anita
OL,7,FRoddick is now huge, which has
OL,8,Fexpanded the competition for The Body
OL,9,FShop.
OL,11,F"I really hope they make it through
OL,12,Fbecause they are an important
OL,13,Fretailer, and important brand and an
OL,14,Fimportant part of British culture,"
OL,15,Fshe added.
OL,17,FRetail analyst Sofie Willmott from
OL,18,FGlobalData retail thinks that the
OL,19,Fcompany has struggled to engage with a
OL,20,Fyounger viewer over the years.
