OL,3,CThe Body Shop owners set to call in
OL,4,Cadministrators
OL,6,F"The beauty market is really tough at
OL,7,Fthe moment. It's evident on social
OL,8,Fmedia, you can see brands fighting for
OL,9,Fattention.
OL,11,F"If it were to cut some stores, The
OL,12,FBody Shop may be able to spend more on
OL,13,Fmarketing and get some younger
OL,14,Fcustomers in."
OL,16,FActor Adjoa Andoh, best known for
OL,17,Fplaying Lady Danbury in the Netflix
OL,18,Fseries Bridgerton, said there is an
OL,19,F'emotional attachment' to the brand
OL,20,Ffor many people.
