OL,6,F"Generations of us have been going to
OL,7,FThe Body Shop. I think we get an
OL,8,Femotional attachment to these places,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,FActor Adjoa Andoh, best known for
OL,12,Fplaying Lady Danbury in Bridgerton,
OL,13,Fsaid there is an 'emotional
OL,14,Fattachment' to the brand for many
OL,15,Fpeople
OL,17,F"I remember being thrilled when one
OL,18,Fopened in Brixton, we felt anchored in
OL,19,Fthat way. I feel that many feel
OL,20,Fsimilarly.
