OL,6,F"Not only do they like their produce,
OL,7,Fbut they like what their produce is
OL,8,Fconnected to.
OL,10,F"The fact that you can refill your
OL,11,Fbottles, especially when you're
OL,12,Fthinking about climate change. I think
OL,13,Ffor all those reasons we've become
OL,14,Fquite attached to it, it's become part
OL,15,Fof how we shop".
OL,17,FThe Body Shop and Aurelius declined to
OL,18,Fcomment.
